  "title": "Using sticky traps to monitor populations of Trichogramma egg parasitoids",
  "abstract": "In a field study in 1995 in Andhra Pradesh, the Trichogramma population was monitored with sticky traps in a sorghum/pigeon pea intercrop. The parasitoid density peaked in sorghum but was low in pigeon peas at the same time as that of Helicoverpa armigera peaked in both crops.",
